wiki.summary: "The Fame" is the title track on the debut album by American pop recording artist Lady Gaga.

track.name: The Fame

''Fame, fame, baby. The fame, fame. We live for the fame, fame, baby. Isn't it a shame, shame?''

Fame, Fame, baby, the Fame, Fame ♥♥♥
Don't ask me how or whyyyyy (or why) ♥
One of the best Gaga songs. :) [3]
Cause we got a taste for champagne and endless fortune ♥
